<div class="bash-example">
    <pre><code class="language-bash">curl --request GET \
    --get "http://localhost/api/v1/accounts/departments?search=architecto&amp;per_page=16&amp;column_sort=architecto&amp;sort_direction=architecto" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
